text.__SUMMARY__: Psychotria dolichantha is a flora species in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Jamaica.
text.References: World Conservation Monitoring Centre (1998). "Psychotria dolichantha". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T35946A9969632. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T35946A9969632.en. Retrieved 16 December 2017.
